  <description type="morphology">Plants coarse, straggling. Stems usually finely papillate. Leaf blades narrowly lanceolate, usually 3–6 cm, widest near base. Pedicels usually reflexed in fruit. Flowers ca. 10 mm diam.; sepals with 3 prominent, ridged veins extending to near apex, narrowly triangular, 3.5–5 mm, longer than 0.5 times capsule length. Capsules straw colored, translucent, usually (3.6–)5–7 mm, 2 times as long as broad. Seeds usually rugulose. 2n = 52.</description>
